==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Piecework
<hw>Piece"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Work done by the
piece or job; work paid for at a rate based on the amount of work done,
rather than on the time employed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The reaping was <qex>piecework</qex>, at so much per acre.</q>
<rj><qau>R. Jefferies.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pied</ent>⟦br⟧
